metadata.name: Feelz #00001
metadata.description: EmojiCardz-Feelz is a revolutionary idea of bringing emotions on blockchain. With 10,000 carefully created tokens,  We are preparing to disrupt the collectibles market by providing an experience of collecting and sharing emotions. We're bringing emotions and feelings to the metaverse in order to find a new way to express ourselves in a digital world. Each feelingz lives in a unique blockchain bordering the rarity that surrounds it. Find out more on our Link below
